ActBudget Implementation Act, 2018, No. 1
SubjectOrder Fixing January 31, 2020 or the Day on Which the United Kingdom Ceases to be a Member State of the European Union, as the Day on Which Section 220 of that Act comes into Force
PrecisOrder Fixing January 31, 2020 or the date on which the United Kingdom ceases to be a member state of the European Union pursuant to Article 50 of the Treaty on European Union, whichever is later, as the day on which section 220 of the BUDGET IMPLEMENTATION ACT, 2018, NO.1, chapter 12 of the Statutes of Canada, 2018, COMES INTO FORCE.
